# Analytics schema enforcement (Phase 8).
# Rejects schema_version=2 events missing client_event_id or event_time.
# Safe to enable because Unity AnalyticsManager auto-injects both fields.
# Set to "false" only if a legacy client that sends schema_version=2 without
# those fields is still in production.
